{
  "page": "Lord of the Waters",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Warning</b> <br /> This information has thus far been released in a sample chapter for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, and might therefore not be in finalized form. Keep in mind that the content as described below is still subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Lord of the Waters</b> is the self-fashioned title of a <a href=\"/index.php/Pirate\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Pirate\">pirate</a> king.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_the_Waters&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Winds_of_Winter\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_the_Waters&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Winds of Winter\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Valena_Toland\" title=\"Valena Toland\">Valena Toland</a> tells <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_Martell\" title=\"Arianne Martell\">Arianne Martell</a> that the Lord of the Waters has installed himself on <a href=\"/index.php/Torturer%27s_Deep\" title=\"Torturer&#39;s Deep\">Torturer's Deep</a>. He has \"monstrous large\" three-decker warships.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Presumably he is <a href=\"/index.php/Aurane_Waters\" title=\"Aurane Waters\">Aurane Waters</a>, former <a href=\"/index.php/Grand_admiral\" title=\"Grand admiral\">grand admiral</a> to Queen Regent <a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei Lannister</a>, who ordered the construction of <a href=\"/index.php/Cersei%27s_dromonds\" title=\"Cersei&#39;s dromonds\">a fleet of dromonds</a> and crewed them with criminals,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> then fled <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> with the warships after Cersei's arrest.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> The title may be a play on Aurane's <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a> surname of Waters and one of the titles of his father's house, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Velaryon\" title=\"House Velaryon\">House Velaryon</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Tides\" title=\"Lord of the Tides\">Lord of the Tides</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_the_Waters&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_I_(The_Winds_of_Winter)\" title=\"Arianne I (The Winds of Winter)\">Arianne I</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_17\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 17\">Chapter 17</a>, Cersei IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_43\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 43\">Chapter 43</a>, Cersei X.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404010035\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.017 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.018 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 191/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8881/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 2489/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 515/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1240/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    9.145      1 -total\n 48.93%    4.475      2 Template:Ref\n 29.97%    2.741      2 Template:Ref/core\n